<h1>Architecture overview</h1><section class="card"><h2>Target state</h2><p>Systems connect through an integration fabric made of Spring Boot APIs, Apache Camel routes, Kafka-compatible event topics, MariaDB operational state, and Keycloak OIDC identity.</p></section><section class="card"><h2>Boundaries</h2><p>Connector credentials are references only. Tenant-owned records include tenant_id and are queried through tenant-scoped endpoints.</p></section>
